{"id":560051,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/05/【麻辣总局】和习爷爷说心里话/","date":"2017-05-29T03:27:36Z","modified":"2017-05-29T03:27:36Z","title":"【麻辣总局】和习爷爷说心里话","content":"<p>近期，全国各地学校“为深入学习宣传贯彻以习近平同志为核心的党中央对少年儿童的关怀和希望，鼓励少年儿童围绕喜迎党的十九大，自主表达纯真的情感和真实的心声。”争相举办“喜迎十九大——我向习爷爷说句心里话”的主题活动。其中一副来源不详的小学生作品引起网友热转，该作品将天安门城楼的毛泽东像替换为了习近平像，而被称为“高级黑”。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/image_uploaded_from_ios.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-560054\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/image_uploaded_from_ios.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/image_uploaded_from_ios.jpg 800w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/image_uploaded_from_ios-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/image_uploaded_from_ios-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-560053\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/image_uploaded_from_ios-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/image_uploaded_from_ios-1.jpg 800w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/image_uploaded_from_ios-1-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/image_uploaded_from_ios-1-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>来自5月29日10时40分微博测试提示：</p>\n<p>根据相关法律法规和政策，“习爷爷”搜索结果未予显示。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,13789],"tags":[13222,30666,10969,9091,24186]}